module INT-COMMON [digest(OCTyTIVLLuEPxSBufJ4syiOk/6/QJYFX19vt6qJhB5U=), org.kframework.attributes.Location(Location(1218,1,1365,10)), org.kframework.attributes.Source(Source(/nix/store/d8fck8kh57jp0d43k3w1ssjd1r7nn0s3-k-7.1.297-c376de7d91e5f14cff13b7e32e1c997983a2859b/include/kframework/builtin/domains.md))]

  imports BOOL
  syntax priority ~Int_ > _^Int_ _^%Int__ > _divInt_ _%Int_ _/Int_ _modInt_ _*Int_ > _-Int_ _+Int_ > _<<Int_ _>>Int_ > _&Int_ > _xorInt_ > _|Int_

  syntax associativity left _xorInt_
  syntax associativity left _modInt_
  syntax associativity left _divInt_ _%Int_ _/Int_ _modInt_ _*Int_

  syntax associativity left _^Int_
  syntax associativity left _^%Int__
  syntax associativity left _>>Int_
  syntax associativity left _<<Int_ _>>Int_
  syntax associativity left _<<Int_

  syntax associativity left _-Int_ _+Int_
  syntax associativity left _-Int_
  syntax associativity left _+Int_
  syntax associativity left _*Int_
  syntax associativity left _&Int_
  syntax associativity left _%Int_
  syntax K ::= "srandInt" "(" Int ")" [function, hook(INT.srand), impure]
  syntax Int ::= Int "|Int" Int [comm, function, hook(INT.or), left, smtlib(orInt), symbol(_|Int_), total]
  syntax Int ::= Int "xorInt" Int [comm, function, hook(INT.xor), left, smtlib(xorInt), symbol(_xorInt_), total]
  syntax Int ::= Int "modInt" Int [function, hook(INT.emod), left, smt-hook(mod), symbol(_modInt_)]
  syntax Int ::= Int "divInt" Int [function, hook(INT.ediv), left, smt-hook(div), symbol(_divInt_)]
  syntax Int ::= Int "^Int" Int [function, hook(INT.pow), left, smt-hook(^), symbol(_^Int_)]
  syntax Int ::= Int "^%Int" Int Int [function, hook(INT.powmod), left, smt-hook((mod (^ #1 #2) #3)), symbol(_^%Int__)]
  syntax Int ::= Int ">>Int" Int [function, hook(INT.shr), left, smtlib(shrInt), symbol(_>>Int_)]
  syntax Int ::= Int "<<Int" Int [function, hook(INT.shl), left, smtlib(shlInt), symbol(_<<Int_)]
  syntax Int ::= Int "/Int" Int [function, hook(INT.tdiv), left, smt-hook((ite (or (= 0 (mod #1 #2)) (>= #1 0)) (div #1 #2) (ite (> #2 0) (+ (div #1 #2) 1) (- (div #1 #2) 1)))), symbol(_/Int_)]
  syntax Int ::= Int "-Int" Int [function, hook(INT.sub), left, smt-hook(-), symbol(_-Int_), total]
  syntax Int ::= Int "+Int" Int [comm, function, hook(INT.add), left, smt-hook(+), symbol(_+Int_), total]
  syntax Int ::= Int "*Int" Int [comm, function, hook(INT.mul), left, smt-hook(*), symbol(_*Int_), total]
  syntax Int ::= Int "&Int" Int [comm, function, hook(INT.and), left, smtlib(andInt), symbol(_&Int_), total]
  syntax Int ::= Int "%Int" Int [function, hook(INT.tmod), left, smt-hook((ite (or (= 0 (mod #1 #2)) (>= #1 0)) (mod #1 #2) (ite (> #2 0) (- (mod #1 #2) #2) (+ (mod #1 #2) #2)))), symbol(_%Int_)]
  syntax Int ::= "~Int" Int [function, hook(INT.not), smtlib(notInt), symbol(~Int_), total]
  syntax Int ::= "signExtendBitRangeInt" "(" Int "," index:Int "," length:Int ")" [function, hook(INT.signExtendBitRange)]
  syntax Int ::= "randInt" "(" Int ")" [function, hook(INT.rand), impure]
  syntax Int ::= "minInt" "(" Int "," Int ")" [function, hook(INT.min), smt-hook((ite (< #1 #2) #1 #2)), total]
  syntax Int ::= "maxInt" "(" Int "," Int ")" [function, hook(INT.max), smt-hook((ite (< #1 #2) #2 #1)), total]
  syntax Int ::= "log2Int" "(" Int ")" [function, hook(INT.log2)]
  syntax Int ::= "bitRangeInt" "(" Int "," index:Int "," length:Int ")" [function, hook(INT.bitRange)]
  syntax Int ::= "absInt" "(" Int ")" [function, hook(INT.abs), smt-hook((ite (< #1 0) (- 0 #1) #1)), total]
  syntax Bool ::= Int "dividesInt" Int [function]
  syntax Bool ::= Int ">Int" Int [function, hook(INT.gt), smt-hook(>), symbol(_>Int_), total]
  syntax Bool ::= Int ">=Int" Int [function, hook(INT.ge), smt-hook(>=), symbol(_>=Int_), total]
  syntax Bool ::= Int "==Int" Int [comm, function, hook(INT.eq), smt-hook(=), symbol(_==Int_), total]
  syntax Bool ::= Int "=/=Int" Int [comm, function, hook(INT.ne), smt-hook(distinct), symbol(_=/=Int_), total]
  syntax Bool ::= Int "<Int" Int [function, hook(INT.lt), smt-hook(<), symbol(_<Int_), total]
  syntax Bool ::= Int "<=Int" Int [function, hook(INT.le), smt-hook(<=), symbol(_<=Int_), total]

module ML-SYNTAX [digest(ZsgmbGSR5GSMCQkS36ExpzTOLiSYqFQ8HDK6/xk/9M0=), not-lr1, org.kframework.attributes.Location(Location(135,1,160,10)), org.kframework.attributes.Source(Source(/nix/store/d8fck8kh57jp0d43k3w1ssjd1r7nn0s3-k-7.1.297-c376de7d91e5f14cff13b7e32e1c997983a2859b/include/kframework/builtin/kast.md))]
  imports SORT-K
  syntax {Sort} Sort ::= Sort "#Or" Sort [assoc, comm, format(%i%1%d%n%2%n%i%3%d), group(mlOp), left, mlOp, symbol(#Or), unit(#Bottom)]
  syntax {Sort} Sort ::= Sort "#Implies" Sort [format(%i%1%d%n%2%n%i%3%d), group(mlImplies, mlOp), mlOp, symbol(#Implies)]
  syntax {Sort} Sort ::= Sort "#And" Sort [assoc, comm, format(%i%1%d%n%2%n%i%3%d), group(mlAnd, mlOp), left, mlOp, symbol(#And), unit(#Top)]
  syntax {Sort} Sort ::= "#wEF" "(" Sort ")" [group(mlOp), mlOp, symbol(weakExistsFinally)]
  syntax {Sort} Sort ::= "#wAF" "(" Sort ")" [group(mlOp), mlOp, symbol(weakAlwaysFinally)]
  syntax {Sort} Sort ::= "#Top" [group(mlUnary), symbol(#Top)]
  syntax {Sort} Sort ::= "#Not" "(" Sort ")" [group(mlUnary, mlOp), mlOp, symbol(#Not)]
  syntax {Sort} Sort ::= "#Bottom" [group(mlUnary), symbol(#Bottom)]
  syntax {Sort} Sort ::= "#AG" "(" Sort ")" [group(mlOp), mlOp, symbol(#AG)]
  syntax {Sort1, Sort2} Sort2 ::= "{" Sort1 "#Equals" Sort1 "}" [comm, format(%1%i%n%2%d%n%3%i%n%4%d%n%5), group(mlEquals, mlOp), mlOp, symbol(#Equals)]
  syntax {Sort1, Sort2} Sort2 ::= "#Forall" Sort1 "." Sort2 [group(mlQuantifier, mlOp), mlBinder, mlOp, symbol(#Forall)]
  syntax {Sort1, Sort2} Sort2 ::= "#Floor" "(" Sort1 ")" [group(mlUnary, mlOp), mlOp, symbol(#Floor)]
  syntax {Sort1, Sort2} Sort2 ::= "#Exists" Sort1 "." Sort2 [group(mlQuantifier, mlOp), mlBinder, mlOp, symbol(#Exists)]
  syntax {Sort1, Sort2} Sort2 ::= "#Ceil" "(" Sort1 ")" [group(mlUnary, mlOp), mlOp, symbol(#Ceil)]
  syntax priority #Implies > #Forall #Exists
  syntax priority #Ceil #Floor #Top #Not #Bottom > #Equals > #And
  syntax priority #And > #Or > #Implies
  syntax associativity left #Or
  syntax associativity left #And
endmodule
